You're right…

264
00:14:48,254 --> 00:14:49,388
He looks just like Yabuuchi.

265
00:14:54,426 --> 00:14:56,896
Please don't worry about me.

266
00:14:56,962 --> 00:14:58,264
I'm so sorry.

267
00:14:59,198 --> 00:15:01,667
I was trying to subdue the situation,

268
00:15:01,734 --> 00:15:04,770
