that we didn't need to know.

269
00:15:11,310 --> 00:15:12,144
Mr. Haie.

270
00:15:13,512 --> 00:15:14,380
You know,

271
00:15:15,648 --> 00:15:18,984
I want to give Mr. Masaki

272
