all of Yabuuchi's assets.

273
00:15:21,987 --> 00:15:23,622
All of it?

274
00:15:24,556 --> 00:15:27,459
-Mrs. Sagami, calm down.
-I am calm.

275
00:15:30,829 --> 00:15:32,498
More like,

276
00:15:33,332 --> 00:15:35,234
I had an inkling

277
00:15:36,101 --> 00:15:37,569
that someone like

278
00:15:38,203 --> 00:15:40,139
Mr. Masaki existed.

279
00:15:42,374 --> 00:15:43,575
You can call it

280
00:15:44,677 --> 00:15:45,844
a wife's instincts.

281
00:15:51,350 --> 00:15:53,218
Is that right…

282
00:15:53,919 --> 00:15:56,555
So I was already thinking about
throwing away all of

283
00:15:56,622 --> 00:15:58,991
Yabuuchi's things
even before all of this happened.

284
00:16:00,426 --> 00:16:04,430
His important little awards and medals,
inheritance, and everything.

285
00:16:09,034 --> 00:16:10,569
You said that

286
00:16:11,236 --> 00:16:13,806
you were going to keep the fact that
Mr. Masaki is

287
00:16:15,007 --> 00:16:17,142
his real illegitimate son a secret.

288
00:16:17,743 --> 00:16:18,744
But…

289
00:16:19,745 --> 00:16:22,281
is that really okay?

290
00:16:24,216 --> 00:16:25,918
I feel like

291
00:16:27,019 --> 00:16:28,220
the right thing to do

292
00:16:29,588 --> 00:16:32,725
is to make Yabuuchi's scandal
known to the public.

293
00:16:32,791 --> 00:16:33,892
-Excuse me.
-But…

294
00:16:34,994 --> 00:16:37,563
I know I'm in no place to say this,

295
00:16:37,629 --> 00:16:39,365
but I believe a family's memories,

296
00:16:40,199 --> 00:16:43,068
whether they're positive or negative,

297
00:16:43,836 --> 00:16:47,006
are best kept within the family.

298
00:16:49,775 --> 00:16:51,443
You have every right to be mad,

299
00:16:51,510 --> 00:16:53,545
but this issue is going to be
an easy target

300
00:16:53,612 --> 00:16:55,414
for the press and public.

301
00:16:56,081 --> 00:16:58,717
I think it's best that you avoid
getting even more

302
00:16:58,784 --> 00:17:00,753
insensitive reporters interviewing you.

303
00:17:11,296 --> 00:17:12,498
That's true.

304
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:15,968
I guess

305
00:17:17,169 --> 00:17:19,304
you're right, Mr. Haie.

306
00:17:21,773 --> 00:17:25,344
I am sorry for upsetting you.

307
00:17:25,411 --> 00:17:26,412
It's nothing.

308
00:17:28,781 --> 00:17:30,516
You know,

309
00:17:30,582 --> 00:17:33,519
something has always been bothering me.

310
00:17:39,391 --> 00:17:40,726
This photo…

311
00:17:43,162 --> 00:17:44,730
I wondered who took it.

312
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:50,502
His eyes look so kind, don't they?

313
00:18:00,145 --> 00:18:01,413
Well,

314
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:03,215
I actually feel relieved

315
00:18:04,116 --> 00:18:05,584
now that the mystery is solved.

316
00:18:08,921 --> 00:18:10,122
Professor Ogikubo,

317
00:18:11,423 --> 00:18:12,958
thank you very much

318
00:18:13,025 --> 00:18:14,626
