322
00:18:32,010 --> 00:18:33,145
Although,

323
00:18:34,146 --> 00:18:36,715
the amount of time
you can spend healthy is limited.

324
00:18:39,017 --> 00:18:41,286
I want to enjoy

325
00:18:43,255 --> 00:18:46,725
that limited amount of time
to the best of my ability.

326
00:18:49,328 --> 00:18:51,763
Not as Yabuuchi's wife,

327
00:18:53,065 --> 00:18:54,299
but a free…

328
00:18:58,370 --> 00:19:00,005
new life.

329
00:19:05,410 --> 00:19:06,745
-Again?
-Again.

330
00:19:06,812 --> 00:19:08,180
Ready…

331
00:19:11,483 --> 00:19:13,152
30 PASSENGERS DEAD
900 MILLION YEN IN COMPENSATION

332
00:19:13,218 --> 00:19:15,754
DRIVER FELL ASLEEP AT THE WHEEL
OVERWORKED

333
00:19:21,527 --> 00:19:22,961
Mom,

334
00:19:23,996 --> 00:19:25,898
