472
00:29:04,943 --> 00:29:05,944
Dad.

473
00:29:06,978 --> 00:29:07,812
Nao?

474
00:29:10,048 --> 00:29:11,249
Mom?

475
00:29:11,316 --> 00:29:13,051
HAIE'S MOTHER
MIYUKI HAIE

