481
00:29:37,709 --> 00:29:38,676
Thank you.

482
00:29:56,494 --> 00:29:57,662
Mom.

483
00:29:59,631 --> 00:30:01,800
I've never told you this before,

484
00:30:01,866 --> 00:30:03,234
but there is

485
00:30:03,301 --> 00:30:04,803
something I want you to know.

486
00:30:08,540 --> 00:30:11,376
When I'm done with
what I'm working on right now,

487
00:30:12,043 --> 00:30:13,011
I plan

488
00:30:14,279 --> 00:30:16,080
to settle the score for Dad.

489
00:30:18,716 --> 00:30:20,552
That man will do

490
00:30:20,618 --> 00:30:23,054
anything to put me, you,

491
00:30:23,121 --> 00:30:25,356
and Dad through anguish.

492
00:30:26,124 --> 00:30:27,292
But

493
00:30:28,359 --> 00:30:31,196
if I make the truth
about Dad's accident known,

494
00:30:32,964 --> 00:30:34,399
I can end Jidori.

495
00:30:37,068 --> 00:30:39,938
-Then you'll be able to live more freely.
-Nao.

496
00:30:42,774 --> 00:30:44,042
I am

497
00:30:45,076 --> 00:30:48,279
happy enough just seeing you

498
00:30:48,980 --> 00:30:50,748
alive and well.

499
00:30:51,649 --> 00:30:52,517
What?

500
00:30:54,652 --> 00:30:55,987
You are the only thing

501
00:30:56,621 --> 00:30:58,423
I look forward to in life.

502
00:31:01,359 --> 00:31:02,493
You are

503
00:31:03,895 --> 00:31:05,663
the only reason why

504
00:31:06,698 --> 00:31:08,566
I am living right now.

505
00:31:11,035 --> 00:31:11,870
So…

506
00:31:13,671 --> 00:31:15,874
you don't have to fight anyone.

507
00:31:18,810 --> 00:31:20,845
Stop being haunted by the past.

508
00:31:23,982 --> 00:31:26,150
I want you to be free.

509
00:31:28,853 --> 00:31:30,188
Mom…

510
00:31:37,161 --> 00:31:38,529
But I…

511
00:31:41,266 --> 00:31:44,135
want to protect Dad's honor.

512
00:31:46,237 --> 00:31:48,206
If I don't do it, who else will?

513
00:31:48,907 --> 00:31:50,008
Nao.

514
00:31:53,511 --> 00:31:54,545
Dad…

515
00:31:56,581 --> 00:31:58,316
I promise to settle the score

516
00:31:58,850 --> 00:31:59,984
for you.

517
00:32:20,738 --> 00:32:23,741
Shaking off reporters is a piece of cake.

518
00:32:32,951 --> 00:32:33,885
Hello.

519
00:32:34,786 --> 00:32:36,988
Thank you for your invitation.

520
00:32:37,055 --> 00:32:39,157
This is Masaki.

521
00:32:41,826 --> 00:32:42,860
Nice to meet you.

522
00:32:43,428 --> 00:32:45,029
I'm Masaki Shimada.

523
00:32:47,632 --> 00:32:49,133
I'm Yabuuchi.

524
00:32:49,801 --> 00:32:50,702
Please come in.

525
00:32:52,770 --> 00:32:53,805
Thank you.

526
00:32:56,908 --> 00:32:58,076
