529
00:33:05,350 --> 00:33:07,719
No, I should be the one to apologize.

530
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:12,557
I'm terribly sorry for what Yabuuchi did.

531
00:33:14,792 --> 00:33:16,060
I'm sure

532
00:33:16,928 --> 00:33:19,464
