533
00:33:19,530 --> 00:33:23,034
It's okay,
I was always told that my father was dead.

534
00:33:29,974 --> 00:33:31,776
Go ahead and eat while it's hot.

535
00:33:31,843 --> 00:33:33,177
-Come on.
-Okay.

536
00:33:33,244 --> 00:33:34,278
Thank you for the food.

537
00:33:35,146 --> 00:33:36,948
I hope you like it.

538
00:33:41,119 --> 00:33:42,053
